title: Morning Joe 3/19/21
description: President Joe Biden and Vice President Kamala Harris will travel to Atlanta Friday to meet with Asian American community leaders and state lawmakers in the wake of the spa shootings that left eight people dead, six of whom were women of Asian descent.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
